 <h1 style="font-family:'Playfair Display',serif;font-size:clamp(1.8rem,4.5vw,3rem);font-weight:700;margin-bottom:18px;line-height:1.15;">Extended Stay Hotel<br>in Vernal, Utah</h1>
 <p style="font-size:1.05rem;line-height:1.7;opacity:.88;max-width:620px;margin:0 auto 24px;font-weight:300;">Need more than a night or two? Best Western Vernal Inn is Vernal's premier extended-stay hotel — with weekly rates from $588, full kitchenettes, free hot breakfast, and the amenities long-term guests actually need. Whether you're here for two weeks or two months, this is home.</p>
